<li id="cite_note-11"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11" title="">^</a></b> Hindi jaina, from Sanskrit jaina-, "relating to the saints", from <span lang="sa-Latn" title="International Alphabet of Sanskrit Transliteration" class="Unicode" style="white-space:normal; text-decoration: none" xml:lang="sa-Latn">jinaḥ</span>, "saint, victor", from jayati, "he conquers". <a href="http://dictionary.reference.com/search?q=Jains&amp;r=66" class="external text" title="http://dictionary.reference.com/search?q=Jains&amp;r=66" rel="nofollow">dictionary.com entry</a></li>
