acy">Theocracy</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Religious_violence" title="Religious violence">Violence</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/Religious_persecution" title="Religious persecution">persecution</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Religious_terrorism" title="Religious terrorism">terrorism</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Religious_war" title="Religious war">war</a>)</span></div>
